---
title: One-Pot Italian Beef & Tomato Soup with Kale, Pearled Couscous & Garlic Bread
description: No matter the weather, it’s tough not to crave a big bowl of soup (i.e. the culinary equivalent of a bear hug). Enter this hearty, soul-warming veggie rendition. It’s chock-full of goodness—that is to say carrots, onion, crushed tomatoes, a bevvy of Italian herbs and spices, chewy couscous, and tender kale. And because no good brothy bowl is complete without something delicious for dunking, we’re also throwing in a side of toasty, buttery garlic bread. Soup’s on!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/62c58d6f4319a7d0bc0f62d2-a3fa52d9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pot-italian-beef-tomato-soup-62c58d6f4319a7d0bc0f62d2-94fa81b8.pdf
